<div style="margin-bottom:20px;">
  <div style="font-size:15px; font-weight:800; color:#2E2E38; margin-bottom:6px;">Retrè An Kou</div>
  <div style="font-size:13px; color:#5D6345;">N ap trete retrè MonCash ou.</div>
</div>

<div style="background:#E8EDE0; border:2px solid #5D6345; border-radius:14px; padding:16px; margin-bottom:16px; text-align:center;">
  <div style="color:#5D6345; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1px; margin-bottom:8px;">Montan Retire</div>
  <div style="color:#991b1b; font-size:28px; font-weight:900; letter-spacing:-1px;">
    - <%= @amount_display %>
  </div>
  <div style="margin-top:4px;">
    <span style="display:inline-block; background:#2E2E38; color:#C5A059; font-size:10px; font-weight:800; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:10px; letter-spacing:0.5px;">
      MONCASH
    </span>
  </div>
</div>

<div style="background:#fff; border:1px solid #d9d6c4; border-radius:12px; padding:12px; margin-bottom:16px;">
  <table width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
    <tr>
      <td style="color:#5D6345; font-size:12px; font-weight:600; padding-bottom:8px;">Nimewo MonCash</td>
      <td style="color:#2E2E38; font-weight:700; text-align:right; padding-bottom:8px; font-size:12px;"><%= @phone %></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="color:#5D6345; font-size:12px; font-weight:600; padding-bottom:8px;">Metòd</td>
      <td style="font-weight:700; text-align:right; padding-bottom:8px; font-size:12px; color:<%= @instant ? '#C5A059' : '#166534' %>;">
        <%= @instant ? "Instant" : "Estanda (48 èdtan)" %>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="color:#5D6345; font-size:12px; font-weight:600;">Frè (<%= @instant ? "1.5% instant" : "1% estanda" %>)</td>
      <td style="color:#C5A059; font-weight:700; text-align:right; font-size:12px;">HTG <%= format('%.0f', @fee.to_f) %></td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</div>

<div style="font-size:13px; color:#5D6345; line-height:1.6;">
  <% if @instant %>
    Retrè instant ou ap trete kounye a. Ou ap resevwa lajan an sou MonCash ou nan kèk minit.
  <% else %>
    Retrè estanda ou anrejistre. Ou ap resevwa lajan an sou MonCash ou nan 48 èdtan.
  <% end %>
</div>
